    {% if page.url == "/" %}
      <h1>The free, secure and fast DNS service <strong class="text-gradient">you need for a better browsing experience</strong></h1>
      <p>Use our DNS over HTTPS/TLS/QUIC/Tor features to encrypt your DNS traffic.</p>
      
    {% elif page.url == "/id/" %}
      <h1>Secure and fast DNS service <strong class="text-gradient">for Indonesian Internet</strong> to <strong class="text-gradient text-gradient-golden">protect your privacy</strong> online</h1>
      <p>Keep your online activity private with our secure and fast DNS service.</p>

    {% elif page.url == "/family/" %}
      <h1>Protect Your Family and Kids from <strong class="text-gradient">Cyber Threats</strong> by <strong class="text-gradient">Blocking</strong> access to Websites with <strong class="text-gradient text-gradient-red">Undesirable Content</strong></h1>
      <p>DNS for Family blocks malware, adware, gambling, fakenews, and NSFW sites using well-curated lists provided by the open source community.</p>
    {% endif %}

    <p>
